(CHEERS AND APPLAUSE)

14:37.967 --> 14:41.767
Teller, you can see I took out
six black cards and six red cards.

14:41.833 --> 14:44.433
I'm gonna ask you to give those
cards a wash,

14:44.500 --> 14:46.367
Vegas style. Just mix them up.

